txt.en: Enter the the Clutch-hollow and destroy the worm eggs within.\n\nSpeak to Hórin to travel to the Clutch-hollow.

'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].\n\n'We have found a den of worms within the mountains. What's left of Scatha's foul brood lay their eggs and raise their young there. I ask that you infiltrate their lair and destroy their eggs before more can hatch! For the Zhélruka!'
DNT - 'Get in there and break some eggs!'
'Good work, [placeholder]. Better to deal with those devils BEFORE they start breathing fire at us!'
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Hórin for your reward!
Deep in the Wyrmsgráf, what remains of Scatha's brood makes their den....\n\nYour mission is to infiltrate the Clutch-hollow and destroy the worm eggs within.
At low health, monsters in this mission will attempt to end their own life to damage and apply a fear effect to those nearby.
You have been tasked with destroying the unhatched eggs in the Clutch-hollow.
